message.name: ERR_DELETE_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_RELEASED
message.locale: This determination package has been released and cannot be deleted.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_COMBINATION_EXISTS
message.locale: This Age range overlaps with another determination package with this Gender and Product within this determination configuration.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_DELETED
message.locale: The determination configuration to which you are trying to add this determination package has been deleted.Therefore this determination package cannot be created.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_AGE_MUST_INTEGER
message.locale: Age Should be in Integer.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATIONPACKAGE_DEFAULT_COMBINATION_EXISTS
message.locale: There can only be one determination package with no Product, Min Age, Max Age or Gender specified for each determination configuration.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATIONPACKAGE_UNIQUE_COMBINATION_EXISTS
message.locale: Each Gender, Age range and Product combination for a determination package must be unique for that determination configuration.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATIONPACKAGE_NAME_EMPTY
message.locale: Name must be entered.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATIONPACKAGE_XRV_NAME_ALREADY_EXISTS
message.locale: A determination package with this Name already exists.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATIONPACKAGE_MINAGE_MAXAGE_COMBINATION_INVALID
message.locale: The Maximum Age should be greater than or equal to the Minimum Age.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATIONPACKAGE_MINAGE_INVALID
message.locale: If entered the Minimum Age should be zero or greater.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATIONPACKAGE_MAXAGE_INVALID
message.locale: If entered the Maximum Age should be zero or greater.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_CANCELLED
message.locale: The determination to which you are trying to add this determination package has been deleted. Therefore this determination package cannot be created.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_RELEASED
message.locale: This version has been released and cannot be modified. To modify the determination package you must first create a new version.

message.name: ERR_DELETE_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_HAS_QUESTIONNAIRES
message.locale: This determination package version has associated questionnaires and cannot be deleted.

message.name: ERR_DELETE_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_HAS_DMS
message.locale: This determination package version has associated decision matrices and cannot be deleted.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATIONCONFIGURATION_ENDDATE_EARLIER_THAN_CURRENTBUSINESSDATE
message.locale: This determination package cannot be released as the end date of the determination configuration %1d is earlier than current date.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_INEDIT
message.locale: A new determination package version cannot be created because the latest version is In Edit.\n You must Release or Delete the latest version before creating a new version.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_IN_RELEASED
message.locale: The determination package has been released and a new questionnaire cannot be added.You must create a new version of the determination package to add a new questionnaire.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_NOT_RELEASED_NO_QUESTIONNAIRE
message.locale: No questionnaire has been associated with this determination package.Create and release a questionnaire for this determination package and then try again.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_NOT_RELEASED_QUESTIONNAIRE_IN_EDIT
message.locale: A questionnaire associated with this determination package is In Edit. Please Release or Delete the In Edit version of this questionnaire and try again.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_RELEASED_NO_MATRICES
message.locale: No decision matrix has been associated with this determination package.Create and release a decision matrix for this determination package and then try again.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_RELEASED_MATRICES_IN_EDIT
message.locale: A decision matrix associated with this determination package is In Edit. Please Release or Delete the In Edit version of this decision matrix and try again.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_RELEASED_DETERMINATION_START_DATE_IN_FUTURE
message.locale: This determination package cannot be released as the Start Date of the determination configuration %1d is in the future.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_IS_ALREADY_RELEASED
message.locale: This determination package has already been released.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIRE_ALREADY_EXIST
message.locale: This questionnaire is already associated with this determination package version.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIRE_CANNOT_REMOVE_PACKAGE_INEDIT
message.locale: The determination package has been released and cannot be modified. You must create a new version of the determination package to remove a questionnaire.

message.name: ERR_DP_ALREADY_RELEASED_MATRIX_CANNOT_BE_ADDED
message.locale: The determination package has been released and a new decision matrix cannot be added. You must create a new version of the determination package to add a new decision matrix.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_RELEASED_DELETE_MATRIX
message.locale: This determination package has been released and cannot be modified. To remove the decision matrix a new In Edit version of the package must be created.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_EXISTS_FOR_THIS_DETERMINATIONCONFIGURATION_WITH_OPTIONAL_CRITERIA_AGE
message.locale: A determination package already exists for this determination configuration with the optional criteria Age. Another determination package cannot be created with a different optional criteria.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_EXISTS_FOR_THIS_DETERMINATIONCONFIGURATION_WITH_OPTIONAL_CRITERIA_GENDER
message.locale: A determination package already exists for this determination configuration with the optional criteria Gender. Another determination package cannot be created with a different optional criteria.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_EXISTS_FOR_THIS_DETERMINATIONCONFIGURATION_WITH_OPTIONAL_CRITERIA_FOR_PRODUCT_GENDER
message.locale: A determination package already exists on this determination configuration for this product with the optional criteria Gender. Another determination package cannot be created for this product with a different optional criteria.

message.name: ERR_DETERMINATION_PACKAGE_EXISTS_FOR_THIS_DETERMINATIONCONFIGURATION_WITH_OPTIONAL_CRITERIA_FOR_PRODUCT_AGE
message.locale: A determination package already exists on this determination configuration for this product with the optional criteria Age. Another determination package cannot be created for this product with a different optional criteria.
